    <owl:DatatypeProperty rdf:about="https://city-artificial-intelligence.github.io/diso/ontology#spdxLicenseExpression">
        <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string"/>
        <rdfs:comment>The licence of a dataset expressed as an SPDX licence expression, recorded verbatim. Captures compound expressions (e.g. &apos;MIT AND CC-BY-4.0&apos;) and the value &apos;NOASSERTION&apos; where no licence could be established.</rdfs:comment>
